OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers in
OL,6,Fthe south easing this evening, but
OL,7,Fthickening cloud in the north and
OL,8,Fnortheast could bring light showers
OL,9,Flater in the night. Less warm than
OL,10,Fprevious nights.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FLargely fine with bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells, most prolonged in the
OL,14,Ffar west. Cloud spreading southwards
OL,15,Fcould bring isolated showers that may
OL,16,Fturn thundery. Breezy along eastern
OL,17,Fcoasts. Less hot.
